{"word":"G1856 - ἐξωθέω - exōthéō - ex-o-theh'-o - Drive out","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξωθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exōthéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-o-theh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Drive out</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துரத்திவிடு, ஒட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to thrust out; expel from one's abode"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <b>&#x03C9;&#x0313;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>o&#x0304;theo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>push</i>); to <i>expel</i>; by implication to <i>propel:</i> - drive out, thrust in.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}